Freewing had just reached the African continent, and he was looking for the 
old Alliance base, when he found another ruined base. Not knowing it's 
origin, he studied its interior for a few clicks, then he decended into the 
ruined hull. He prepared his missiles upon entry, in case any hostile 
characters popped out of the shadows. He began to explore the base...
